I love cars, but more than that I LOVE sharing the experience with friends and family, NOW YOU. One of my objectives with Turo is to share this unique experience with others, for a fair price of course.

I have a passion for helping people realize their dreams or experience life uniquely through Turo, even if it's just renting one of my cars for a few days. I promise to do my best to assist, accommodate, and deliver the best rental experience possible. From delivery to drop off, I will ensure each of my guests is attended to from beginning to end. I also realize that I am human and that all cars may have unexpected issues, however I vow to take care of them to the best of my ability should they ever arise during your rental.

Besides helping my Turo guests with their car rentals, I really enjoy experiencing different cultures through food, drinks, and travels throughout the world.

I hope you will afford me the opportunity to host you here in my hometown of Dallas, Texas!

Welcome to Lonestar Auto Rentals, formerly known as DFW Lonestar Rental! We pride ourselves on being a trustworthy and reliable car rental service with an impeccable 5-star rating. With over 100 vehicles in our fleet, we offer an extensive selection to cater to all your transportation needs.

At our company, customer satisfaction is our top priority, which is why we have a dedicated 24/7 customer service team that is always ready to assist you. Whether you have questions, need assistance during your trip, or require support with booking adjustments, our friendly and knowledgeable team is just a text away.

We understand that plans can change, so we offer flexible booking and trip adjustment options to ensure a stress-free experience. Life can be unpredictable, but with us, you can easily modify your reservation or make changes to your trip to fit your evolving needs.

Convenience is key, and we have you covered with multiple locations and our contactless lockbox access system for convenient pickups and drop-offs. No matter where you are, you can count on us to provide a seamless rental experience. We strive to make renting a vehicle hassle-free and convenient so you can focus on enjoying your journey.

With our commitment to exceptional customer service, an extensive fleet of over 100 vehicles, 24/7 support, flexible booking options, and convenient multiple locations, we guarantee an outstanding experience every time you choose us for your car rental needs.

Join our satisfied customers and experience the difference for yourself. Book with Lonestar Auto Rentals today and embark on your next adventure with confidence!

Welcome to Pioneer Star Rentals!

As a car-sharing host, we're proud to introduce our fleet, which is managed by a friend combo, Nate and Taggart. Currently, we've got 11 cars available on Turo, and we're adding more every week.

If you're after a reliable host, look no further. Our commitment to running the Turo fleet full-time is clear from our reviews. Nate handles guest communication and is pretty much available 24/7 to help with questions, worries, or anything unexpected. On the other side of things, Taggart takes care of the vehicles. He makes sure they're clean between bookings and keeps the whole fleet in good shape.

All our cars have instant booking turned on, and they come with remote key exchanges, so you don't need to worry about meeting up in person to get the keys. It's all about making things easy and flexible for you.

Now, our cars aren't flawless, and they might show a bit of wear and tear from regular use. Just so you know, they're not like those brand-new, showroom-ready rides. But, if what you're looking for is a well-kept, dependable, and clean car at a good value, our fleet is spot on.

Even though our cars do show some signs of wear and tear, we're on top of keeping them in good shape. Every car gets a thorough cleaning and disinfection after each rental, making sure your ride is safe and comfy for the journey. Our cars will get you where you need to go, without a doubt, and at a wallet-friendly price.

Our Turo profile speaks for itself when it comes to being great hosts. If you want reliability, you've found it with Pioneer Star Rentals.

We can't wait to help you hit the road.  Enjoy the ride!

Cheers,
Nate & Taggart
